        <div id="inventory-management-system" class="modal glass-card">
            <div class="modal-content">
                <span class="close-button" onclick="document.getElementById('skye-inventory-modal').style.display='none'">&times;</span>
                <h3>Inventory Management System</h3>
                <p>This **Inventory Management System** is a robust desktop application built with **Python** and its powerful **PyQt5** framework for the graphical user interface. It leverages **SQLite** as a lightweight and efficient database solution for seamless data management.</p>
                <p>The system provides comprehensive functionalities for inventory control, including adding new items, viewing and searching existing stock, updating item details, and managing user accounts with distinct roles. As a UNISA student passionate about sustainable technology and backend development, this project showcases my ability to develop a full-featured application, integrate database solutions, and create intuitive user interfaces, ensuring efficient and reliable inventory operations.</p>
                <div class="modal-tags tags">
                    <span class="highlight-tag"><i class="fab fa-python icon-spacing"></i> Python</span>
                    <span class="highlight-tag"><i class="fas fa-desktop icon-spacing"></i> PyQt5 (GUI)</span>
