        <div id="school-system-modal" class="modal glass-card">
            <div class="modal-content">
                <span class="close-button">&times;</span>
                <h3>School Management System</h3>
                <p>The <strong>School Management System</strong> is a powerful <strong>Java-based</strong> application designed to automate and manage core academic and administrative operations within an educational institution. It integrates seamlessly with a <strong>relational database</strong> (e.g., JDBC) to handle student records, faculty information, course management, attendance tracking, grading, and scheduling.</p>
                <p>This project demonstrates advanced <strong>backend development</strong> skills, including API design, data validation, authentication mechanisms and robust error handling. The system's architecture prioritizes efficiency, scalability, and data security, ensuring confidential information is protected. It aims to reduce manual workload, improve administrative efficiency, and provide a centralized platform for school management, showcasing my ability to build comprehensive enterprise-level applications.</p>
                <div class="modal-tags tags">
                    <span class="highlight-tag"><i class="fab fa-java icon-spacing"></i> Java</span>
                    <span class="highlight-tag"><i class="fas fa-database icon-spacing"></i> SQL Database</span>
